pageContext.claim: “You look at the unemployment rate for youth, and you look at the fact -- for youth, so important -- remember, three, four years ago they couldn't -- there was no work. Now it's the lowest they've ever had.”
pageContext.analysis: The unemployment rate for all ages has gone lower in previous decades. Trump falsely claims "there was no work" three or four years ago for the youngest segment of the working-age population.
